author: USA TODAY NETWORK, Joel Shannon, David Robinson and Lorenzo Reyes, USA TODAY NETWORK
title: New York is at war with the coronavirus. Expect the same across the US, experts warn.
description: What is unfolding in New York City offers a case study in how the virus attacks all aspects of life, as well as what can be done to beat it back.
content:
New York City built a makeshift morgue for the expected influx of coronavirus deaths.
